            <p th:sID="novel1_letter4_chapter18_div4_div18_p17"/> We had agreed to 
        <seg th:sID="__F" part="F"/>
            <seg th:eID="__F" part="F"/>
    the Rhine in a boat from 
        <seg th:sID="__F" part="F"/>
