    a day at Manheim, 
        <seg th:sID="__F" part="F"/>
            <seg th:eID="__F" part="F"/>
    on the fifth from our departure from 
        <seg th:sID="__F" part="F"/>
            <seg th:eID="__F" part="F"/>
    arrived at Mayence. The course of the Rhine below Mayence becomes much more picturesque. The river descends 
        <seg th:sID="__F" part="F"/>
